-/*
- * pp_alt (measure-first candidate #2, writel-audit). The seq-kick producer
- * S_POINTER POINTER field is hardcoded 0 every kick, so every task programs
- * ping-pong group 0 while the vendor sets S_POINTER once and the PC advances
